/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/06072011027.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/06072011028.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\nThis is what the gun looks like after adjusting the &quot;Adjustable Comb&quot; to my liking<br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/07072011029.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\nI have raised the comb a little and increased the cast of the shotgun.<br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/07072011030.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/07072011031.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/07072011032.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/07072011033.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/07072011035.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/07072011036.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns/Adjustable%20Comb%20on%20Baikal%20IZH-27%20or%20MP-27EM-1C/07072011037.jpg" border="0" alt="" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src="http://i998.photobucket.com/albums/af103/12gauge-pakguns