(0x7642436d735f41727469636c655f70616765746578745f3133312e3437363030363064336265336530383664366435373435343565393066383434, 1479026191, 1478939791, 0, '1', 'a:4:{s:5:"pages";a:1:{i:1;s:8381:"Gentlemen AOA! I had an opportunity to visit the Turkish Army Museum and I photographed the Ottomans collection of hand guns which I am posting for your viewing. These photographs include a few carbines / rifles / two old vintage machineguns as well. To explain the weapon, I am using exactly the same terminology as was used there in the museum. These terminologies might have been in use then but may sound strange to us now. For example, you will quite frequently see the explanation as &quot;Revolving Pistols&quot;. Please ignore them. Similarly, I am using the same spellings as have been used there at the museum. I have photographed the explanations as well, but including them in the post would have created lot of confusion. Therefore I am writing the explanations but for the pictures which are self explanatory there is no caption. There are a total of 129 handguns but I think it will require lot of stamina to post them all at once so I shall be posting them all in couple of days.<br />\n<b>Happy Viewing</b><br />\n<br />\n1. Self Loading Pistol, German Model 1896<br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=Ts7aEa0" target="_blank"><img src="http://s2.postimage.org/7aEa0.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. Ten Barrelled Pin Fire Pistol, German (Reform), Model 1911<br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfwVeA" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fwVeA.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n3. Four Barrelled Pin Fire Pistol German (Reform), Model 1911<br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfxlG9" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fxlG9.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. Two Barrelled Pistol, German, 20th Century<br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfxvEJ" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fxvEJ.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n5. Pocket Pistol, French, End of 19th Century<br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfxI7r" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fxI7r.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n 6. Details Inside the Pictures<br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfyz_A" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fyz_A.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfyHu0" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fyHu0.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfyOYr" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fyOYr.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfyTXJ" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fyTXJ.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfz2Wi" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fz2Wi.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfzfp0" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fzfp0.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfzrSJ" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fzrSJ.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfEQ69" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fEQ69.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. Multi Barrelled Percussion Pistols<br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfBqAS" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fBqAS.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=gxfBS1r" target="_blank"><img src="http://s1.postimage.org/fBS1r.jpg" border="0" alt